data.title: Camp Rock Cast and Crew
data.meta_description: Camp Rock Cast and Crew - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The movie Camp Rock focuses on a summer music camp called Camp Rock. It stars Demi Lovato as Mitchie Torres and Joe Jonas as Shane Gray. The movie was directed by Matthew Diamond and written by Karin Gist, Regina Y. Hicks, and Julie Brown. It showcases the campers' musical talents and a budding romance between Mitchie and Shane.
